  "title": "Junior System & Network Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Ascenxus Pte Ltd is an ICT infrastructure solutions provider delivering system and network integration services for enterprise environments. We design, implement, and support infrastructure platforms that keep business systems reliable and connected.</p><p>We are looking for a Junior System & Network Integration Engineer to join our delivery team. This role is suitable for fresh graduates or early-career professionals who want hands-on experience in system and network implementation work.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities: </strong></p><ol><li><strong>System Support -</strong> Assist in deploying and supporting Windows servers, virtual machines, and basic infrastructure components under guidance from senior engineers.</li><li><strong>Network Support -</strong> Assist in configuring and supporting LAN and WAN connectivity, IP addressing, and basic firewall or VPN setups.</li><li><strong>Integration & Implementation Work</strong> - Support system and network integration activities during project deployment, upgrades, and migrations.</li><li><strong>Operational Support</strong> - Perform Level 1 / 2 troubleshooting for system and network issues and escalate where required.</li><li><strong>Documentation & Diagrams</strong> - Maintain technical documentation, change records, and system / network diagrams.</li></ol><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Information Technology, Computer Science, Engineering, or a related discipline (Fresh graduates are welcome to apply)</li><li>Basic understanding of computer systems and networking concepts (e.g. Windows OS, IP addressing, TCP/IP, LAN/WAN basics)</li><li>Exposure to Windows Server, virtualization, or networking through studies, labs, or internships is an advantage</li><li>Willingness to learn and work hands-on with system and network integration projects</li><li>Able to follow structured procedures, document work, and escalate issues clearly</li><li>Good attitude, sense of responsibility, and ability to work in a team environment</li></ul><p></p>",
